Invisible radio player - is a very simple and lightweight flash radio player 
for any webpage. All you need is add one line on your page. IRP can play 
Icecast and Shoutcast streams.

<embed src="http://alexxz.github.com/Invisible-radio-player/irp.swf " width="1" height="1" 
    wmode="transparent" flashvars="autoplay=1&url=http://91.121.182.57:9080/; "></embed>

If you need to control this player just see examples page.


To compile this project you will need mtasc compiler.
To run test example you will need http server because flash sequrity policies.

For some reason every Shoutcast link must finished with semicolon(;)
